<inglise>Airport administrations shall obtain approval from the Border Guard for applications to alter the schedules of scheduled passenger air services and for the schedules of new passenger air services which are to be opened and promptly inform the Border Guard of the receipt of approval notices concerning the schedules from the air navigation authorities. </inglise>
